        <num>33-34A-12</num>
        <content>
          <p>The Commissioner shall adopt rules and regulations which include disclosures for the benefit of the warranty holder, record keeping, and procedures for public complaints.Such rules and regulations shall also include the conditions under which surplus lines insurers may be rejected for the purpose of underwriting vehicle protection product warranty agreements.</p>
